<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.1.9">
<l>tuṉṉi maṇṇum viṇṇāṭun tōṉṟā tiruḷāy mūṭiyanāḷ</l>
<l>aṉṉa māki yarumaṟaika ḷaruḷic ceyta vamalaṉiṭam</l>
<l>miṉṉu cōti navamaṇiyum vēyiṉ muttuñ cāmaraiyum</l>
<l>poṉṉum poṉṉi koṇarntalaikkum puḷḷam pūtaṅ kuṭitāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of the faultless one who, as a swan, uttered the rare Vedas,</l>
<l>The day that the earth and land of heaven, being compressed,</l>
<l rend="indent">having become invisible, were hidden in darkness,</l>
<l>Is Puḷḷampūtankuṭi where the Poṉṉi [River] crashes bringing gold and jalap,</l>
<l>Bamboo pearls and nine jewels of shimmering light.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
